47
00:05:14,452 --> 00:05:16,522
{\an1}Look into my eye.

48
00:05:19,292 --> 00:05:22,128
{\an1}You are inside my
genjutsu right now.

49
00:05:23,095 --> 00:05:25,599
{\an1}It is still a blank canvas,
