136
00:10:34,745 --> 00:10:36,847
{\an1}You mean that you
know about my eyes?

137
00:10:37,748 --> 00:10:41,485
{\an1}You are the reincarnation of
the Sage of the Six Paths,

138
00:10:41,518 --> 00:10:44,522
{\an1}who dreamed of world
